\SM[double]\SE[19]Congratulations on clearing it!! You have
conquered this shitty game! \!\SE[1]Thank you for
playing...!!

\SE[8]So, umm... Did you play until the end? How was it?
\SE[9]I hope it was made well...
\SE[3]Well... If I can be honest with my thoughts...

\SM[stamp]\SE[36]It was... the best...! \SE[45]To satisfy
the lust that was aroused by tormenting monsters, and to
embrace Laura...! It's irresistible...! \SM[rock]\SE[66]Just
thinking about it makes me feel like I'm going crazy...!!

\SE[61]The second half had an excessive amount of brain
drugs and it was dangerous... \!\SE[66]Thank you for such an
amazing game...!

\SE[88]God-tier game...!!!? \!\SE[71]The shitty game I made
turned into a god-tier game...!?

\SE[27]Uu... I'm so glad...!! \SM[rock]\SE[29]You worked
hard to make it... I'm so glad!!

\SM[nod]\SE[0]Ah... that's right. \SE[3]Do you have any
requests for elements like this? \SM[nod]\SE[0]Is it better
to have prizes after all?

\SE[2]Hmm... I think I prefer experiences over prizes.
\SE[15]I feel a sense of accomplishment in improving
myself...

\SE[15]Improvement... a sense of accomplishment...
\!\SE[17]I see! \. I see...!! \!\SE[15]So scores, ratings,
and competition can lead to increased motivation...!!

\SE[0]But, I'm sure that's where experience points come
in. \SE[0]We'll probably need some random ideas and it seems
like it will take time...

\SE[15]That's right...! \!\SE[15]I wonder if everyone
would be happy if we released more varieties of Laura...!

\SE[30]Eh...! \SE[30]Bunny Laura, \SE[61]Nurse Laura,
[3]Police Officer Laura, [4]Maid Laura, and [5]Young Girl
Laura...!!

\SE[60]If we prepare various types of Laura...!
\!\SM[nod]\SE[74]Won't all the users be satisfied...!

\SE[14]Hmm... \!I feel like Lunaroa's personal bias is too
strong.... \!\SE[51]But, she did say it was the first time
she called it a god-tier game....

\SE[16]Alright, leave it to me!! \!\SE[15]I'll consider if
it can be implemented...!

\SM[double]\SE[77]Really!? \!\SE[16]\!Yay! I'm looking
forward to its completion...!!

\SE[24]Y-You're looking forward to it that much...?
\SE[24]Ehehe, don't be embarrassed...
\SE[1]Ah, this is the prize for this time.
\SE[0]Alright, I'll let you out of the game!
